'Résultat de la requête:'

SQL> SELECT DISTINCT
  2      c.nom,
  3      c.prenom
  4  FROM client c
  5  WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  6      SELECT 1
  7      FROM categ_velo cv
  8      WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  9          SELECT 1
 10          FROM depot d
 11          JOIN detail_velo dv ON dv.id_velo = d.id_velo
 12          WHERE d.id_client = c.id_client
 13            AND dv.id_categ = cv.id_categ
 14      )
 15  )
 16  ORDER BY c.nom, c.prenom;

NOM                  PRENOM
-------------------- --------------------
Dupont               Jean

